          "id": "medmcqa-a2a4182e-7356-4270-88e8-40626e40a414",
          "text": "A patient is to undergo angiography for unstable angina. His routine evaluation revealed his serum creatinine to be elevated. All of the following can be used to prevent contrast nephropathy, EXCEPT:",
