          "id": "medmcqa-b7faa894-2206-45ff-8fda-5f0744708a46",
          "text": "A patient taking 120 ml alcohol everyday since last 12 years is brought to the hospital by his wife and is diagnosed to have alcohol dependent syndrome. Which of the following drug should be avoided in the management?",
