          "explanation": "Corpus Callosum is commonly involved in:- *Adrenoleukodystrophy *Marchiaa Bignami Disease *Progressive Multifocal Leukoencephalopathy *Diffuse Axonal Injury *CNS lymphoma *Glioblastoma multiformis(Butterfly Glioma)",
