          "explanation": "Ans. D: 2 protons, 2 neutrons Alpha paicles are simple helium nuclei (i.e. consisting of 2 protons and 2 neutrons) Remember: Alpha rays: Most ionizing Gamma rays: Maximum penetration power Cesium-137, cobalt and radium emits predominantly: Gamma rays"
