          "explanation": "Treatment modalities for liver secondaries \n\nLiver transplant (in patients with single lesion < 5 cm or three or fewer, lesions < 3 cm)\nHepatic artery embolization & chemotherapy (chemoembolization)\nIntralesional in situ ablation via ultrasound-guided\n\n         Percutaneous ethanol (alcohol) injection\n         Cryotherapy\n         Radiofrequency ablation\n         Microwave coagulation therapy"
