          "id": "medmcqa-de87853d-e5da-45cc-88fd-e977fab9562e",
          "text": "New born male baby presented with congestive heart failure. On examination enlarged fontanelles, a loud cranial bruit and following radiological finding was noted-the mostly likely diagnosis:",
