          "explanation": "Ans: C i.e. High resolution CT scan Conditions and IOC MRI is IOC for superior sulcus/ pancoast tumour HRCT is IOC for interstitial lung disease and Bronchiectasis V/Q scan is 2\"d IOC for pulmonary embolism (CT with I/V contrast is first IOC for pulmonary embolism)"
