          "explanation": "O-16,O-17, O -18 are stable radioisotopes of oxygen.\nC-12, C-13, are stable radioisotopes of carbon (not C-14).\nP-31, is stable radioisotopes of phosphorus (not P-32).\n1-125 is radioactive form of iodine (not stable)."
