          "explanation": "According to Inverse square law in radiation, the intensity of radiation is inversely propoional to the square of distance from the source. Rapidly dividing cells , which are less differentiated are actually more radiosensitive Amongst the body cells, the most sensitive are spermatogonia and the least sensitive are nerve cells and muscle fibres",
